{"title":"秋声新吟——看程派新秀专场演出","authors":["徐笠翁"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋声新吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——看程派新秀专场演出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐笠翁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑟瑟雁声吟梦心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皑皑雪地立程门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾无俗念情入戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有新歌夜惊魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长悲山壑啼白日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独泪胡笳吊黄昏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数尽亭外春秋雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终见菊园御霜人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺苑喜添山菊魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋声幸有天鹤音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袖浪似歇云千缕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韵丝未断雷万钧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚柔相济多新境，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品技双绝少凡尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红帷三降人不去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声依旧伴泪痕！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":10,"page_end":10}